headline: Nordson Corporation Declares Third Quarter Dividend for Fiscal Year 2025
summary: WESTLAKE, Ohio, June 05, 2025--Nordson Corporation (Nasdaq: NDSN) today announced that its board of directors declared a fiscal year 2025 third quarter cash dividend in the amount of $0.78 per common share, payable on July 3, 2025, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on June 19, 2025.
